d
d=1
\begin{align*}\frac{3^{2m+1}+1}4&=dx\\{}\\3^{2m+1}-1&=dy\end{align*}\;\;\;\;\;\;,\;\;d,x,y\in\Bbb Z
\frac12=dx-\frac{dy}4=\frac d4\left(4x-y\right)\implies2=d(4x-y)\implies d=1\;\;\vee\;\;2
\,d=2\;
